WEBVTT

00:00:00.435 --> 00:00:04.613
Moram nešto da vam priznam,

00:00:04.613 --> 00:00:07.876
ali prije toga želim

00:00:07.876 --> 00:00:11.469
da vi meni nešto priznate.

00:00:11.469 --> 00:00:14.557
Podignite ruku ukoliko ste 
u posljednjih godinu dana

00:00:14.557 --> 00:00:17.971
doživjeli relativno slab stres.

00:00:17.971 --> 00:00:20.604
Iko?

00:00:20.604 --> 00:00:23.133
A umjerenu količinu stresa?

00:00:23.133 --> 00:00:26.441
Ko je iskusio jako stresnu situaciju?

00:00:26.441 --> 00:00:28.849
Da. Ja takođe.

00:00:28.849 --> 00:00:31.113
Ali to nije ono što sam htjela da priznam.